dcterms:description: Daily realized estimates of the S&P 500 from January 2000 to January 2022, used to calibrate an ordinary Ornstein-Uhlenbeck process and a fractional Ornstein-Uhlenbeck process.

dcterms:description: Monthly observations of the Consumer Price Index for All Urban Consumers (CPI-U) in the United States from January 1950 to November 2022, used to calibrate a Gamma random walk and a regime-switching AR(1) process.
